title: Sharing is Caring
itunes:title: Sharing is Caring
description:
Today on the show we opened the phone lines to see is our listeners have any problem with a relative dating an ex of theirs, after The Game said in an interview that he does not mind if any of his friends or relatives mess with one of his exes. Also, Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee" and Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a man that stole a car and try to sell back the car to the owner.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
